item.description: Bo-Wun, a software engineer, is interested in artificial intelligence and software engineering. Actually, writing something valuable is another interest for Bo-Wun. This is a place to post some notes, good articles, and some experience. Feel free to connect Bo-Wun via github or send him an email. Of course, you can also comment below direclty :) Hope this website can bring you the energy of progress. Last, never give up, because we have much more potential than we imagined !
